m $1,000 to to several hundred thousand."SOURCES: Associated Press, CNET,https://apnews.com/d716aac4ad744b4cae3c6b13dce12d7ehttps://www.cnet.com/news/homeland-security-detected-phone-spying-devices-in-dc/***]]></description>
