" if he or she is nearer to the opponent's goal line than the ball, and nearer to the opponent's goal line than the second to last opponent, or, if the referee determines that you have participated in area of active play."SOURCES: http://www.fifa.com/about-fifa/official-documents/law-regulations/***]]></description>
