sections are only powered when a car or truck is overhead." "When the vehicle drives off the electric rails, the system calculates the energy consumption and debits the driver."SOURCES: The Guardian, Inhabitathttps://www.theguardian.com/environment/2018/apr/12/worlds-first-electrified-road-for-charging-vehicles-opens-in-swedenhttps://inhabitat.com/worlds-first-electric-road-that-charges-moving-vehicles-debuts-in-sweden/***]]></description>
